    Claude --> Decision[Decision engine<br/>per-regulator score<br/>sanctions force-BLOCK<br/>BLOCK→FLAG downgrade<br/>worst-case aggregate]
    Decision --> Audit[(Postgres audit log<br/>claude_raw_output<br/>system_prompt_hash<br/>reg_snapshot_id)]
    Decision --> Telegram[Telegram alert<br/>FLAG / BLOCK only<br/>fire-and-forget]
    Decision --> Response[JSON response<br/>decision, score, confidence<br/>rule_references]
    FastBlock --> Response

